{
  "stem": "26983.12",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 67.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He belonged to the Czech Brothers, this is special, elite Protestant group, the best of the Czech tradition, which goes back to the Czech Brothers many hundreds years ago.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he thought about it, that children may come back from the camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He thought that there are many children in Theresienstadt because he knew these Jewish children who went to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only after the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During nobody could visit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody could visit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But during the war, in '40, '41, he, with the help of his friends, organized food, mainly milk, to-- into Jewish families where there were newborn babies because the Germans didn't allow to give--",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--milk to Jewish newborn babies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was denounced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got called to the chief of Gestapo in Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the chief of Gestapo asked him, is it true, Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Peter, that you are distributing milk?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't you know that it's forbidden?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So instead, like all of them, he didn't say, well, I didn't, or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's my human duty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that made such an impression on the chief of the Gestapo that he let him free-- not only in this case, but all during the war, he was somehow free from the persecution of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This man took over former German castles in the neighborhood of Prague-- the castle of [NON-ENGLISH] and so on, which belonged to a German aristocracy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The castle we have been as children, belonged to the former minister of finance and he, with the help of his friends, changed it into recreation homes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Therefore, again, we were tremendously lucky to come in a peaceful surrounding with lovely people who really cared for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The other children came to DP camps, sometimes for--",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
